CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 16 reads: "Charming Trio...Among the hundreds of guests at the birthday testimonial were three close friends of Mrs. Vann: Mrs. Henry Lindsay, Mrs. Marjorie McKenzie Lawson of Washington, D.C., Courier columnist, and Mrs. Harold Butler"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. Henry Lindsay, Marjorie McKenzie Lawson, and Mrs. Harold Butler, standing in Penn Sheraton hotel for Jessie Vann's birthday party
